section     Installing Hammerspoon
remind      Hammerspoon needs Accessibility access enabling before it can resize windows.

brewfile

clone       github:norm/hammerspoon-config  ~/etc/hammerspoon
symlink     ~/etc/hammerspoon/$HOST.lua     ~/etc/hammerspoon/init.lua
symlink     ~/etc/hammerspoon               ~/.hammerspoon

install     hammerspoon.plist   ~/Library/Preferences/org.hammerspoon.Hammerspoon.plist

loginitem   Hammerspoon
start       Hammerspoon
